\"SE-49496b68-b944-4521-b5d6-883aba53abbc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예를 들어 추석 전이나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3437bc9a-f930-4973-8aa4-cc4a4649ea6b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-27cd4c9f-5936-4845-9afe-2363eab8ccaa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기타 불가항력 천재지변 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2c13bfd5-67d0-4884-a631-b51a3807a7c2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5fb4e1fe-eb5c-405d-832b-c6a1077b6aa9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">으로 지연되는 경우가 종종 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7aaa06a0-d771-4b9d-9034-b4e1111a65cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5f3b4e2a-d17c-43e4-be12-cd547520fc97\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">또한 자사의 기계나 시설의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3ee55f74-a142-4ec7-ace1-7866327bdde7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e72e9720-7d1e-4015-9921-c109a2a36720\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">문제로 지연되면 환불은 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-00db536a-616d-4dbc-8f84-790aa74fff79\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-268d04dd-8332-4fb5-9b4b-400373ab466f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">하지만 지연에 따른 배상은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5cc24e62-d221-477e-a1dc-e60e6f072d6a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09c88ea6-307f-46d0-a5fc-6725977b061e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-59fcb77d-431e-4244-a2cc-963cd7fabb77\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd346dfa-4eed-47f6-a3bb-4745d95fb6dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ed4eb21b-cb34-4deb-9c28-20e6de90b0b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8967d40-879c-4fc7-89ae-da4fb872a1e0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">하지만 항상 최선을 다해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9742ebdb-f167-4236-866f-534906a38072\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a8e453c-69ca-4577-a753-8ca70f9f009d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">납기를 맞추도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7688b0af-86cd-461f-8317-8f2f64224cb2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e3a61e9a-f78b-4c63-83cb-9d2be61d872e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f8f8a9bb-3c95-4f57-8dd5-1946803e5d21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e48c3e83-c73f-40c5-9f76-071b4001b150\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>지연에 따른 배상 책임</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6223e50b-6ad9-4eb7-87a1-cc3a4f289e2b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-26148350-0794-4469-ba32-ca5abaea3ace\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9dddc4ec-4ad7-43a5-92f8-9566fe1fff65\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b224e086-b7dc-4b1d-a8dd-4026f241b617\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 항상</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3db1e3d2-30c6-48f2-abf8-03ef658d113e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0cf1ba79-9b64-41fb-9f2d-b188644b4426\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객의 시간을 가장 중요하게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-479bb7e0-c2cf-41a8-acea-a83ba518b74a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d54b8851-df19-4547-a2f8-188e5ef8255f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f521aa4f-1f65-4349-987d-4beaa91e881e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c715288-1680-4916-9aa7-29d421fee870\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 자사의 돌발적인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0506a444-1e85-40db-90d4-a7951dede6a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08d824e6-c088-46ca-b0af-b1e296b150e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">설비, 인원 사정이나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b946c57f-fde1-413e-ae05-2bc4891637c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-22009c56-ca5a-4eab-82de-a09f6f415b43\" style=\"color:#555555;\">불가항력의 지연 또는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6d0577bd-ef93-48ef-8ad1-d1220f59761d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c58490fa-56cf-48c3-ae31-d9a11b32dd48\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자사 인원의 실수로 인해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3b5a920b-e627-480e-9345-7dcced25ad93\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb8eaaa5-e671-46eb-86a4-b0e989bad60c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">배송이 지연되거나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-646f07b2-a249-4429-a711-7a4ee8b4e379\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-633e06f9-936d-4f0a-9078-65d4f3b1a4d6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">취소되는 경우에는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bc0bcd6e-451c-45fd-a162-a2456bd5cc58\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-107691a2-c348-45e3-9079-273dee656bc6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">환불에 대한 책임을 지겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-131da6a9-86bb-4b70-bca4-61d0ed764106\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3dbdc52b-fd73-4451-b1e6-c1559713f4a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cb1bfe53-394b-4711-89fb-825d74d72e83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-495a3e14-3e91-4d93-bea7-ef70e8f31fdc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 배송 지연에 따른</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f18caf95-2e0e-4a17-8cb3-b9b12c8cadb0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9253aae7-6eab-4870-a216-6bb71e616d5c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">책임보상까지는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f2f5e526-926a-4af3-b598-5a2b48024bbb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ba9e453-272f-4191-b805-2531f7dae622\" style=\"color:#555555;\">지지 않습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e519f739-0b9a-4557-a83e-35a7eb7ac08a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6a10ea77-1c6f-4177-b793-4981c44eaa44\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
